'''''Monty Python & the Quest for the Holy Grail''''' is an [[adventure game]] created by [[7th Level]] in 1996 for [[Microsoft Windows|Windows]]. The game is based on the 1975 film ''[[Monty Python and the Holy Grail]]'' and was the second of three [[Monty Python]] games created by 7th Level.

==Crew==
*''Terry Gillam'' - Director
*''[[Terry Jones]]'' - Director
*''Steve Martino'' - Creative Director
*''Alex Yevgenyev'' - Technical Director
*''Charles Otte'' - Producer
*''Robert Alan Ezrin'' - Executive Producer
*''[[Eric Idle]]'' - Executive Producer / Writing Consultant
*''Hollis Leech'' - Supervising Producer 
*''Jon M. Greenwood'' - Line Producer
*''Bert Jennett'' - Writer
*''Peter Crabb'' - Writing Consultant
*''[[Ron Wasserman]] - Music

